# Challenges

# Group Bowling

## Games Collection [/v1/bowling/games]

### Create game [POST]

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        ```
        {
            "id": 123,
            "created_at": "2016-01-22 19:18:17"
        }
        ```

## Games [/v1/bowling/games/{game_id}]

+ Parameters

  + game_id (required, number)

### Details [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        ```
        [
            {
                "player_id": 1,
                "frames": [
                    {
                        "score": 9,
                        "deliveries": [
                            {
                                "id": 1,
                                "pins_hit": 5
                            },
                            {
                                "id": 2,
                                "pins_hit": 4
                            },
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "score": 6,
                        "deliveries": [
                            {
                                "id": 3,
                                "pins_hit": 5
                            },
                            {
                                "id": 4,
                                "pins_hit": 4
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
        ```

## Player's Deliveries Collection [/v1/bowling/games/{game_id}/players/{player_id}/deliveries]

+ Parameters

  + game_id (required, number)
  + player_id (required, number)

### Details [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        ```
        {
            "frames": [
                {
                    "score": 9,
                    "deliveries": [
                        {
                            "id": 1,
                            "pins_hit": 5
                        },
                        {
                            "id": 2,
                            "pins_hit": 4
                        },
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "score": 6,
                    "deliveries": [
                        {
                            "id": 3,
                            "pins_hit": 5
                        },
                        {
                            "id": 4,
                            "pins_hit": 4
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
        ```

### Create delivery (throw ball) [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        ```
        {
            "pins_hit": 5
        }
        ```

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        ```
        {
            "frames": [
                {
                    "score": null,
                    "deliveries": [
                        {
                            "id": 1,
                            "pins_hit": 5
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
        ```